  "article_text": "A tale of riddles and secrets.\n\nFor those adventurers puzzled by this transmission, a file sent by the ATMTA inc. industries was recently discovered in a probe captured in deep space.\n\nWhen commanded to open, it displays the runestone hologram below, asking for password clues to be inputed.\n\nCuriosity has run rampant across the galaxy as the different races and factions try to answer the enigma with everyone wondering:\n\nWhat will happen when someone manages to decode the final word?",
